# Managed-allowlist policy.
#
# The leading `*` ignores everything in this local Cursor config directory.
# Source is opted in below. Runtime and IDE-produced state stays ignored by
# omission, including:
#   .collabs/       — ephemeral collab runtime; not source
#   .claude/        — local agent state; not source
#   projects/       — local Cursor project state; not source
#   extensions/     — local extension cache/state; not source
#   ide_state.json  — local IDE state; not source
#   skills-cursor/  — Cursor-generated skill payload; not source
#   plugins/        — local plugin cache; not source
#   skills/         — personal skill payload; not source
#   plans/          — local planning scratch; not source
#   subagents/      — local subagent state/transcripts; not source
*

# Cursor config source — tracked
!.gitignore
!CLAUDE.md
!AGENTS.md
!REPOSITORY.md
!_CURSOR.md
!README.md
!.github/
!.github/**
!_core/
!_core/**
!_functions/
!_functions/**
!_generated/
!_generated/**
!_mdc/
!_mdc/**
!_roles/
!_roles/**
!_templates/
!_templates/**
!_tests/
!_tests/**
!commands/
!commands/**
!rules/
!rules/**
!tests/
!tests/**
!tools/
!tools/**
